Html:
When I load my character into Rawr, it shows "Velen's Regalia 2 Piece Bonus" as 0.00 DPS.  I've checked all the relevant buffs and what not, the spec has been imported properly.  It shows the other set bonuses (except for tier 7 bonuses) as a DPS increase.  Any obvious thing I'm missing?  I think this is throwing off my gear optimizing.  Thanks for any help.

Character: Sessea on Antonidas

Go to options, and move the slider for Game/Brain latency a bit until you see the value for the 2 piece change.

 

The reason Rawr may see 2pc t9 as 0 DPS is that it doesnt always give a DPS increase, but it most of the time only ends up being a thing that makes your life simpler./
